    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make sure the essay doesn't just sound like 'some people think this' but actually hits hard on why the current system is fundamentally broken. can you add some points about why the idea of 'meritocracy' is basically just a way to justify the current racial wealth gap? like, how it's used to ignore the actual history of why things are the way they are?",
